snippet.title: Divine Knockout - Official First Look
snippet.description:
Welcome to Divine Knockout. A world of Mythological Multiplayer Mayhem!
DKO is a brand new, fast-paced, Brawler set in a stylized world of Gods and Mythology. DKO combines physics-based combat, a vibrant roster of deities and Third-Person combat that puts you right in the heart of the action!

Launching in 2022 on PC, PlayStation, and Xbox with full cross-platform play and progression!

Sign up for Alpha: http://divineknockout.com

Join the KO Crew:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/dkogame
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/dkogame
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/DKOGame
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@DKOGame
